brand reqlan has a simple brand. Dark rust; and aqua blue pallete. Pink for highlights. Logo is nodular graph/crosshair

extension_brand {
    The extension uses the brand logo from ["../site/public/logo.svg"].
    SVG is used in VS Code where allowed (activity bar); PNG and WebP are generated for marketplace icon, README, and chat participant surfaces.
}

file_icon {
    the file icon for .rq files should use the reqlan logo.
}